reviewText: I didn't even read that it was VHS no use to me

this is a great buy!!! i had all these movies as a kid ( i am now 28 yrs old). i purchased it for my daughter bc i thought she would love it and she did!! she just turned 8 yrs old and she has watched them over and over again. for the price $2.30 well worth it :)
My favorite adventures of Mary-Kate and Ashley Olson too!
I grew up watching the thirty minute Mary-Kate and Ashley videos. So when I saw this recently on Amazon I thought about getting it and I'm glad I did. I love it.
My favorite books all put to one video what can I say? This video is THE BEST EVER!!!
